name: android-security-best-practices.mdc
description: Best practices for security and permissions in Android
globs: **/*.{kt,java,xml}

- Request permissions only when necessary
- Implement runtime permissions correctly
- Handle permission denials gracefully
- Secure sensitive data with encryption
- Implement proper authentication
- Avoid storing sensitive information in SharedPreferences
- Implement certificate pinning for HTTPS
- Check for security vulnerabilities
- Obfuscate code with ProGuard
- Implement proper session management
- Avoid logging sensitive information
- Implement secure networking practices
- Handle crash reporting safely 